              "raw": "{\n  \"text\": \"In my previous role as a project manager, I faced a situation where our team was behind schedule on a critical deliverable. My task was to get us back on track within two weeks. I reorganized the team's priorities and implemented daily standups. As a result, we delivered the project on time and received positive feedback from the client.\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/star_feedback/analyze",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "star_feedback", "analyze"]
            },
            "description": "Start a STAR method analysis job on interview text. Analyzes the response for:\n- Whether it fulfills STAR criteria\n- Percentage breakdown of each component (Situation, Task, Action, Result)\n- Sentence-by-sentence classification\n- Feedback suggestions\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `text` (required): The interview response text to analyze"
          },
          "response": []
